snippet.title: V Rising: Secrets of Gloomrot - Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Enjoy the full gameplay trailer for Secrets of Gloomrot, the upcoming expansion for V Rising that will be available as a free download for owners of the game on May 17.
